      <title>Virgin Media O2 计划英国光纤业务为交易铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/virgin-media-o2-plans-uk-fiber-business-paving-the-way-for-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国互联网提供商 Virgin Media O2 计划将其光纤宽带服务拆分为一个独立的部门，该部门将作为交易平台并挑战现有的英国电信集团 (BT Group Plc)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/virgin-media-o2-plans-uk-fiber-business-paving-the-way-for-deals</guid>
